[SHORT DESC]
If the user faints, the foe's attack loses all of its PP.

[LONG DESC]
<p>If the user faints before its next move, the Pok√©mon that fainted the user will lose all PP in the move they used to KO the user. This does not take into account any end-of-turn damage, such as hail, sandstorm, Leech Seed, status, Doom Desire, or Future Sight.
</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/moves/destiny_bond">Destiny Bond</a> also involves the user fainting.</p>